name: ThePeopleDAO
description:
Inspired by the ConstitutionDAO we want to create a people owned organisation where we go out and collect Real World art and let the DAO decide what to buy and what to do with it afterwards.

Make a profit, create our own museum, or put it on the chain and destroy the real ones... It's all up to you
